# Generated aggregate OpenAPI specs (voyant#2733) — multi-megabyte, unviewable
# on GitHub, rewritten wholesale on any route change. Regenerated on demand via
# `pnpm --filter operator generate:openapi`. The committed, browsable surface is
# the compact per-module files under openapi/{admin,storefront}/.
